VAIFORM — SERVICE / BUSINESS LOGIC RULES

Applies to:
- src/services/**
- src/utils/**

Rules:
- Keep backend business truth centralized.
- Do not move business/timeline/render policy into callers.
- Reuse existing service-layer SSOT rather than duplicating logic in routes/controllers.
- Any service change must preserve current caller-consumed field names unless a contract change is explicitly approved and documented.
- If touching finalize/render/timeline logic, verify the relevant FINALIZE_* docs and current caller-backed behavior first.
- If touching preview/timeline/story logic, preserve backend ownership of:
  - playbackTimelineV1
  - previewReadinessV1
- Do not introduce client-only or route-local timeline truth.
